[Cite as 05/16/2003 Case Announcements #2, 2003-Ohio-2454.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

May 16, 2003

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2002-0400. Citizen Power, Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 01-2736-EL-UNC. On motion for leave to intervene of FirstEnergy Corp. Motion granted.

Cook, J., not participating.

On motion to dismiss of the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Motion granted and cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Lundberg Stratton and O’Connor, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, J., dissents. Cook, J., not participating.
